uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.webapi.dom.utils

Class DOMNodeDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.webapi.dom.utils.DOMNodeDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DOMNode, DOMEventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DOMElementDecorator

    public abstract class DOMNodeDecorator
extends Object
implements DOMNode
    Author:
    Giorgio Orsi Oxford University, Department of Computer Science. This abstract class implements a generic DOMNode decorator (see Decorator Design Pattern at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Decorator_pattern). This generic decorator does not provide any additional method to the DOMNode nor any additional attribute.
